Nov 18 2009 	Loved the Oliver	This central, comfy hotel is very cosy &amp; homely and close to Kensington High Street and Earls Court Tube Station. A 15 to 20-minute walk will bring you to Harrods, Oxford Street, Hyde Park and Piccadilly. Hotel Oliver is in Central London and is well equipped for a low-price stay. Free tea/coffee is available in the breakfast room 24 hours a day, and there is free wireless internet access. There is easy access to buses and trains. The Piccadilly Line service from Earls Court Tube Station goes directly to Heathrow Airport. Secured car parking is available with prior arrangement.	
